about.summary: A nice sphinx theme named 'Cloud', and some related extensions.

name: cloud_sptheme
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.9.4" %}

package:
  name: cloud_sptheme
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: cloud_sptheme-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/c/cloud_sptheme/cloud_sptheme-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 4d665f2f4681140abf8d45b846371d54918207fc397b403f1fa307e8f3394b6c

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  preserve_egg_dir: True
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python
    - sphinx >=1.4

test:
  imports:
    - cloud_sptheme
    - cloud_sptheme.ext

about:
  home: https://bitbucket.org/ecollins/cloud_sptheme
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A nice sphinx theme named 'Cloud', and some related extensions.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
